 "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>Invoice</title>\n<style>\n    body {\n        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n        margin: 0;\n        padding: 0;\n    }\n\n    .container {\n        max-width: 800px;\n        margin: 0 auto;\n        padding: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .header {\n        text-align: left;\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n\n    .logo-container {\n        display: flex;\n        justify-content: space-between;\n    }\n\n    .logo {\n        max-width: 200px;\n    }\n\n    .address {\n        font-size: 12px;\n    }\n\n    .letter {\n        text-align: center;\n        margin-top: 20px;\n    }\n    \n        .line {\n        margin-bottom: 2px;\n  text-align: left\n    }\n   .line2 {\n  margin-bottom:2px;\n  text-align: left\n    }\n\n    .labels {\n        display: inline-block;\n        width: 70px;\n    }\n\n    .colon {\n        margin-right: 10px;\n    }\n  .colon2 {\n        margin-right: 15px;\n    }\n  .colon3 {\n        margin-left: 80px;\n    }\n  .colon4 {\n        margin-left: 10px;\n    }\n  .section p {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-left: 20px;\n            text-indent: -20px; /* Negative text-indent to pull back the second line */\n        }\n        /* Footer Styles */\n    .footer {\n        background-color: #ff8a3a;\n        \n        padding: 20px;\n        text-align: center;\n        border: 1px solid #e8823d;\n    }\n\n    .footer-text {\n        font-weight: bold;\n  \t\tfont-size: 10px;\n        color: white;\n        display: inline-block;\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\">\n            <!--<p>Authorised Sales & Service Parts Dealer</p>-->\n            <div class=\"logo-container\">\n                <div>\n                    <img class=\"logo\" src=\"https://dcautoservices.mydotconsulting.com/files/perodua-logo.png\" alt=\"Company Logo 1\" width=\"200\">\n                    <div class=\"address\">\n                        <!--<b>DC AUTO SERVICES SDN BHD <span style=\"font-size:10px\">(534274-P)</span></b><br>-->\n                        <!--LOT B3A-B7, KAWASAN PERINDUSTRIAN BATU CAVES UTARA<br>-->\n                        <!--68100, BATU CAVES<br>-->\n                        <!--SELANGOR DARUL EHSAN<br>-->\n                        <!--Tel: 0199466683-->\n                        <p>Authorised Sales & Service Parts Dealer</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <!--\n                <img class=\"logo\" src=\"\" alt=\"Company Logo 2\" width=\"200\" height=\"45\">\n                -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"letter\">\n                \n                 <p style=\"text-align: center; text-decoration:underline\">   <strong>DEALER LETTER OF INSTRUCTION TO CREDIT TO PERODUA SALES SDN BHD\u2019S ACCOUNT</strong><br><br></p>\n                   <div class=\"line\">\n                    <span class=\"labels\">Date</span><span class=\"colon\">:</span>\n                    <span>{{ frappe.utils.formatdate(doc.date_issued, \"dd MMMM yyyy\") }}</span>\n                </div><br>\n                   \n                   <p style=\"text-align: left;\">The Head/Manager</p><br>\n                   <p style=\"text-align: left;\">Public Bank Berhad/Public Islamic Bank<br>Berhad Selayang HP Centre/HP Hub/Branch</p><br>\n                     <p style=\"text-align: left;text-decoration:underline\"><b>Crediting of Hire Purchase (HP) disbursement under Release Before Registration (RBR) Arrangement to Perodua Sales Sdn. Bhd.</b></p><br>\n              \n                    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"> We refer to the HP financing provided by your Bank to our car purchaser and would irrevocably request and authorize you to credit that all HP disbursements under RBR arrangement to Perodua Sales Sdn Bhd, current account no: 512017500046 maintained with Maybank Berhad.     \n<br><br></p>\n  \n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"> In consideration of you agreeing to the aforesaid, we hereby confirm that we have no further claim against you in respect of your Hire Purchase Letter of Undertaking and the relevant Invoice and hereby indemnify your Bank against any proceedings/claims/losses/damages and expenses arising from our request/authorization.     \n<br><br></p>\n  \n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"> We further undertake to refund to you the balance of the purchase price with the hiring charges and handling fees so released under the RBR arrangement in the event:-    \n<br><br></p>\n          <p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 40px;text-indent: -20px;\"><b>a)</b>  The said vehicle cannot be registered in the said hirer\u2019s name within 10 days from\n        the date of release for any reason whatsoever;</p>\n        <p style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 40px;text-indent: -20px;\"><b>b)</b>  The ownership claim cannot be effected by Jabatan Pengangkutan Jalan within 10\n        days from the date of release for any reason whatsoever.</p>\n  \n              <br>\n              <p style=\"text-align: left;\">\n                    Thank you.<br><br>\n                Yours faithfully,<br>\n                      <img src=\"https://rohamas.mydotconsulting.com/files/sign%20fairuz.jpg\" width=\"70\" height=\"50\">\n                    <img src=\"https://rohamas.mydotconsulting.com/files/cop%20rohamas%20(1).png\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\"><br>\n                    \n                    -------------------------------------------- <br>\n                    MOHD FAIRUZ BIN MOHD HAMDAN\n                    \n                </p>\n              \n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n     <div class=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"footer-text\">\n            Rohamas Pro Autoserv Sdn Bhd (786823-T), Lot 91517, Persiaran Atmosfera Seksyen U5, 40150 Shah Alam Selangor <br>Tel: 012-8835282\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n",
